track_notes:
Straight-forward descent from Moelwyn Mawr to Rhosydd quarry. This would make a convenient route combined with the quarry access track.

For Allt Fawr follow public right of way (nothing much visible on the ground for most of these) crossing stream. Follow stream uphill to Llyn Cwm-corsiog dam. Head up the ridge north-westerly, to southern edge of Llyn Conglog. Keep following the ridge to arrive a Allt Fawr.

Ground conditions were reasonable for most of this in July.

Executed in descent - route at top could be improved.

From Cwmorthin Road parking area - or take the steam train to Tanygrisiau. Follow quarry track to right turn just before the house / ruins with the Monkey Puzzle tree. Follow the track winding up the slate tips and continue by animal / scrambler track to the ridge. Turn left, following fence line.

Watch out for fissures. One would give a serious fall. Others could at least turn an ankle.

Joining the supposed right of way there is nothing much to see. I came down following the streams, but you would probably do better continuing up straight and turning right along the final bit of ridge.

Park in lay-by just north of the top of the pass (or another just south). 200m up the road take track to left. At some point strike up the hill. I probably went too far. Youre not heading to the big hill, Moel Dyrnogydd, but a little ridge further south, just above the start point. Head to the stile and cross it for nice views from the ridge. Down and up again at Bwlch y Cwm, then up Iwerddon. At SH684479 alternative return track heads down to Llyn Iwerddon reservoir. Final ascent is straightforward.
track_title: From Bwlcg y Gorddinan / Crimea Pass over Iwerddon

track_notes: From parking spot on the A470 follow the very easy track to the tunnel air shaft (SH693483). I dont have many real track points for the next bit - just make something up. I couldnt find much of a path. Through the old wall at the stone that looks like a face, past two small ruins and then to the reservoir dams. Up to the ridge and join my Iwerddon track for final ascent.
track_title: From Bwlch y Gorddinan / Crimea Pass via tunnel shaft track
